The Government Order:

The following employees who have qualified from the selection list of the rank 2022-23 in the cadre of Group 'C' in the Land Records Department are called Deputy Superintendents of Land Records, Group 'B' (Pay Scale S - 15-41800-132300).
Read in Category No. Read Government Order No. 2. Revenue Division Allocation as per the provision in the notification in 1.
Mr. Subhash Kundalikrao Ingole, employee of Section 8 of the said order, has been temporarily promoted to the post of Column Officer.
The post was established at the place mentioned in 4. Now, in this order, Mr. Subhas Kundalikrao Ingole's promoted position has been partially changed to his revised position in Column 5.
It is being done as mentioned in.
2. Read No. The other terms and conditions of the Government Order dated 04.12.2023 in Section 2 shall remain the same.
The Government Order is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
